@node "The Twilight Zone" "The Twilight Zone from 2112"
@toc "The Twilight Zone"
@next "The Twilight Zone"
@prev "The Twilight Zone"
"@{b}@{i}@{fg shadow}@{bg shine}The Twilight Zone@{ub}@{ui}@{fg text}@{bg back}"

 A pleasant faced man steps up to greet you
 He smiles and says he's pleased to meet you
 Beneath his hat the strangeness lies
 Take it off, he's got 3 eyes
 Truth is false and logic lost
 Now the 4th dimension is crossed

 @{b}(Chorus)@{ub}

 @{i}@{fg shine}You have entered the Twilight Zone
 Beyond this world strange things are known
 Use the key, unlock the door
 See what your fate might have in store
 Come explore your dreams' creation
 Enter this world of imagination@{ui}@{fg text}

 You wake up lost in an empty town
 Wondering why no one else is around
 Look up to see a giant boy
